Comment: Round three of the 2007 Wa Open.  After drawing a Sicilian Maroczy bind the night before, I came to the board looking for blood.  Unfortunately for my opponent, I was able to exploit some move order inaccuracies and get the upperhand early and never let go.
The d5 strongpoint systems against the Reti are my favorites to play against.  You are guaranteed a fight from move two!
